'''安祖高顿'''（Angelo Gordon）是一家[[美国|美国]]另类投资管理公司，1988年11月<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/quote/725306Z:US/profile|title=Company Profile for Angelo Gordon & Co LP|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034900/http://www.bloomberg.com/quote/725306Z:US/profile|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IPE Asia Profile">{{cite web|title=Profile|url=http://asia.ipe.com/realestate/investment-manager-profile/angelo-gordon-co_1287.php?article=1|publisher=IPE|accessdate=13 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150112015200/http://asia.ipe.com/realestate/investment-manager-profile/angelo-gordon-co_1287.php?article=1|archivedate=2015年1月12日}}</ref>由约翰·安祖和米高·高顿<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2013-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730194641/http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|dead-url=no}}</ref>创立，二人曾在20世纪80年代共同管理罗斯柴尔德（L.F. Rothschild）的套利部门。<ref name="WallstreetOasis.com/Angelo, Gordon & Co.">{{cite web|title=Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://www.wallstreetoasis.com/company/angelo-gordon-co|website=WallstreetOasis.com|accessdate=13 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407022808/http://www.wallstreetoasis.com/company/angelo-gordon-co|archivedate=2015年4月7日}}</ref><ref>Fabrikant, Geraldine "[http://www.nytimes.com/1988/11/02/business/business-people-2-officials-at-rothschild-leaving-to-start-firm.html BUSINESS PEOPLE; 2 Officials at Rothschild Leaving to Start Firm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1988/11/02/business/business-people-2-officials-at-rothschild-leaving-to-start-firm.html |date=20180713044430 }}." [[New_York_Times|New York Times]], November 2, 1988</ref>

该公司100%由员工持股，已在美国证券交易委员会（SEC）注册，雇用员工约350名。安祖高顿专注于四大投资领域：信贷、房地产、私募股权以及多策略。<ref name="IPE Asia Profile" />在上述广阔领域内，公司提供以下方面的产品：不良债券和非投资级别公司信贷、可转换及合并套利<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>、住宅和消费债务、能源直接贷款<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>、房地产私募股权、房地产债务和贷款、净租赁房地产、私募股权、多策略以及中间市场直接贷款。安祖高顿提供两类投资结构：开放式对冲基金产品以及封闭式私募股权类型产品。<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>

公司总部位于纽约市，在全球（包括：华盛顿特区、旧金山、洛杉矶、芝加哥、休斯顿、伦敦、阿姆斯特丹、香港、首尔以及东京）设有其他办事处。<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek">{{cite web|title=Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co.|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=1689088|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>

==历史==

约翰·安祖与米高·高顿利用其在不良证券、风险套利及可转换套利领域15年的经验，深谋远虑地创立了这家公司。1993年，公司新增了多策略平台，为投资者提供涵盖安祖高顿多种投资策略、并能在市场变化时灵活配置的一站式基金。1998年，公司为扩增不良债券业务，新增杠杆贷款业务。<ref name="Company Overview of Angelo, Gordon & Co. Bloomberg Businessweek" /><ref name="Pi online">{{cite web|title=Through the Cycle: Senior Secured Loans Poised to Perform|url=http://supplement.pionline.com/middle-market-loans/_pdf/LSTA.pdf|publisher=Angelo, Gordon & Co|accessdate=8 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305035441/http://supplement.pionline.com/middle-market-loans/_pdf/LSTA.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

早在1990年，公司就开始通过投资破产房地产公司的不良证券来购买房地产。1993年，随着房地产市场在过多债务的重压下崩溃，公司适时推出机会型房地产策略投资，旨在通过增加营运收入，令相关地产得以改善和重新定位。<ref name="IPE Asia Profile" />

2002年初，公司为了更好地利用其营运伙伴网络，在其房地产策略中添加核心附加房地产，以购买高质量房地产。<ref name="IPE Asia Profile" />从2005年起，公司通过专注于亚洲的机会型房地产策略，扩充房地产业务产品。<ref name="Angelo Gordon Seeks Up to $1 Billion for Asia Real Estate Fund">{{cite web|last1=Hu|first1=Bei|title=Angelo Gordon Seeks Up to $1 Billion for Asia Real Estate Fund|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aPgmi1zQB4DI|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=3 February 2009|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155518/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aPgmi1zQB4DI|dead-url=no}}</ref> 随着2008年全球金融危机和2011年欧洲银行危机的爆发，由于区内价格下跌及流动性大大减弱，安祖高顿将欧洲房地产添加至其策略当中。<ref name="PIE-mag NYC's Angelo, Gordon aims at doubling European exposure to €1bn">{{cite web|title=NYC's Angelo, Gordon aims at doubling European exposure to €1bn|url=http://www.pie-mag.com/articles/7060/nyc-s-angelo-gordon-aims-at-doubling-european-exposure-to-euro-1bn/|publisher=Property Investor Europe|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=9 March 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108140943/http://www.pie-mag.com/articles/7060/nyc-s-angelo-gordon-aims-at-doubling-european-exposure-to-euro-1bn/|archivedate=2015年1月8日}}</ref>

2005年，公司建立净租赁房地产策略，专注于低于投资级别的租户。<ref name="PR Newswire-Angelo, Gordon & Co. Announces Closing of AG Net Lease Realty Fund, L.P. With Commitments of $160 Million">{{cite web|title=Angelo, Gordon & Co. Announces Closing of AG Net Lease Realty Fund, L.P. With Commitments of $160 Million|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/angelo-gordon--co-announces-closing-of-ag-net-lease-realty-fund-lp-with-commitments-of-160-million-53651657.html|publisher=PR Newswire|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=22 January 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924132356/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/angelo-gordon--co-announces-closing-of-ag-net-lease-realty-fund-lp-with-commitments-of-160-million-53651657.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>此外，安祖高顿还进军房地产和信贷的交叉领域，在2006年添加房地产债务<ref name="Hedge Fund Intelligence- Angelo gordon preps cmbs fund">{{cite web|last1=Kenly Waite|first1=Susan|title=Angelo Gordon Preps CMBS Fund|url=http://www.hedgefundintelligence.com/Article/2794072/Angelo-Gordon-preps-CMBS-fund.html|publisher=Hedge Fund Intelligence|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=24 March 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035518/http://www.hedgefundintelligence.com/Article/2794072/Angelo-Gordon-preps-CMBS-fund.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2008年添加住宅和消费债务。<ref name="Forbes Profile Jonathan Lieberman">{{cite web|title=Jonathan Lieberman Profile|url=http://www.forbes.com/profile/jonathan-lieberman/|publisher=Forbes|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108131931/http://www.forbes.com/profile/jonathan-lieberman/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年，安祖高顿在PPIP——公共和私人投资合作计划中，成为与美国财政部、美国联邦储备委员会以及美国联邦存款保险公司合作的九家私人投资公司中的一家。<ref name="US Dept of the Treasury- Public-Private Investment Program">{{cite web|title=Public-Private Investment Program-|url=http://www.treasury.gov/initiatives/financial-stability/TARP-Programs/credit-market-programs/ppip/Pages/purpose-and-overview.aspx|publisher=US Department of the Treasury|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213221607/https://www.treasury.gov/initiatives/financial-stability/TARP-Programs/credit-market-programs/ppip/Pages/purpose-and-overview.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>在全球金融危机爆发后，美国政府与这些精心挑选的公司共同投资，放开冻结的信贷市场。<ref name="Businesswire GE Capital Real Estate and Angelo, Gordon & Co. Pre-Qualified as Legacy Securities Fund Manager for the U.S. Department of the Treasury’s PPIP Program">{{cite web|title=GE Capital Real Estate and Angelo, Gordon & Co. Pre-Qualified as Legacy Securities Fund Manager for the U.S. Department of the Treasury’s PPIP Program|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20090708006079/en/GE-Capital-Real-Estate-Angelo-Gordon-Pre-Qualified#.VK5XN3uPMUN|publisher=Businesswire|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=8 July 2009|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310004015/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20090708006079/en/GE-Capital-Real-Estate-Angelo-Gordon-Pre-Qualified#.VK5XN3uPMUN|dead-url=no}}</ref>该计划取得了巨大成功。<ref name="Pi online">{{cite web|last1=Diamond|first1=Randy|title=PPIP report offers chance for direct comparison of money managers|url=http://www.pionline.com/article/20120514/PRINT/305149946/ppip-report-offers-chance-for-direct-comparison-of-money-managers|website=Pionline.com|publisher=Pensions and Investments|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=14 May 2012}}</ref><ref name="The New York Times-A Big Surprise: Troubled Assets Garner Rewards">{{cite web|last1=Dash|first1=Eric|title=A Big Surprise: Troubled Assets Garner Rewards|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/08/27/business/27toxic.html?_r=1&|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=26 August 2010}}</ref><ref name="Pensions and Investments: Managers make hay with toxic mortgage funds">{{cite web|last1=Comtois|first1=James|title=Managers make hay with toxic mortgage funds|url=http://www.pionline.com/article/20130902/PRINT/309029975/managers-make-hay-with-toxic-mortgage-funds|publisher=Pensions and Investments|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=2 September 2013|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118072204/https://www.pionline.com/article/20130902/PRINT/309029975/managers-make-hay-with-toxic-mortgage-funds|dead-url=no}}</ref>

公司利用2008年金融危机后银行收缩对中小公司贷款的机遇，在2013年开始对能源公司进行优先担保直接贷款<ref name="PE HUB-Angelo Gordon hires energy team for credit investments">{{cite web|title=Angelo Gordon hires energy team for credit investments|url=https://www.pehub.com/2013/10/angelo-gordon-hires-energy-team-credit-investments/|publisher=Reuters PE HUB|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=25 October 2013|archive-date=2017-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624235641/https://www.pehub.com/2013/10/angelo-gordon-hires-energy-team-credit-investments/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在2014年开始为私募股权赞助团体的中间市场借款人提供银行贷款。<ref name="Leveraged Loan- Angelo, Gordon & Co. to launch middle-market direct-lending business">{{cite web|title=Angelo, Gordon & Co. to launch middle-market direct-lending business|url=http://www.leveragedloan.com/angelo-gordon-co-to-launch-middle-market-direct-lending-business/|website=LeveragedLoan.com|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707155540/http://www.leveragedloan.com/angelo-gordon-co-to-launch-middle-market-direct-lending-business/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年10月，罗伦斯·施洛 加入安祖高顿公司担任总裁。<ref name="Bloomberg:NYC Investment Chief Schloss Headed to Angelo, Gordon">{{cite web|last1=Braun|first1=Martin Z.|title=NYC Investment Chief Schloss Headed to Angelo, Gordon|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-09/nyc-chief-investment-officer-schloss-to-join-angelo-gordon.html|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=10 October 2013|archive-date=2015-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110120436/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-09/nyc-chief-investment-officer-schloss-to-join-angelo-gordon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016年3月，罗佗斯. 施洛先生离开了公司。

