==奖项和殊荣==

安祖高顿的投资组合经理近年来在其投资策略方面的出色表现有目共睹。2013年，安祖高顿的CMBS基金和非投资级别公司信贷基金被彭博评为最佳动向固定收益基金（Best Performance for Directional Fixed Income）。<ref name="Bloomberg-The 100 Top-Performing Large Hedge Funds">{{cite web|title=The 100 Top-Performing Large Hedge Funds|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/the-100-top-performing-large-hedge-funds.html|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=4 January 2013|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401133623/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/the-100-top-performing-large-hedge-funds.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2013年<ref>{{cite web|last1=Uhlfelder|first1=Eric|title=Best 100 Hedge Funds|url=http://online.barrons.com/news/articles/SB50001424052748704253204578469283806191260|publisher=Barron's|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=18 May 2013|archive-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709064635/http://online.barrons.com/news/articles/SB50001424052748704253204578469283806191260|dead-url=no}}</ref>和2014年<ref>{{cite web|last1=Uhlfelder|first1=Eric|title=Our Top 100 Hedge Funds|url=http://online.barrons.com/news/articles/SB50001424053111903843804579532040267881368|publisher=Barron's|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=17 May 2014|archive-date=2015-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312220419/http://online.barrons.com/news/articles/SB50001424053111903843804579532040267881368|dead-url=no}}</ref>，RMBS/ABS基金位列Barron’s最优100家对冲基金排名榜（Top 100 Hedge Funds）。安祖高顿的旗舰多策略基金于2012年位列Business Insider100家最成功的对冲基金（100 Most Successful Hedge Funds）名单中<ref>{{cite web|title=The 100 Most Successful Hedge Funds Of 2012|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/100-top-hedge-funds-in-2012-2013-1#68-michael-gordon-and-david-kamin-tied-33|publisher=Business Insider|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403023123/https://www.businessinsider.com/100-top-hedge-funds-in-2012-2013-1#68-michael-gordon-and-david-kamin-tied-33|dead-url=no}}</ref>，于2013年荣获彭博100家表现最佳大型对冲基金（100 Top Performing Large Hedge Funds）<ref>{{cite web|title=The 100 Top-Performing Large Hedge Funds|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/the-100-top-performing-large-hedge-funds.html|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=4 January 2013|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401133623/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-03/the-100-top-performing-large-hedge-funds.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2014年荣获CreditFlux最佳信贷多策略（CreditFlux Best Credit Multistrategy）奖项。<ref>{{cite web|title=CLO Opportunities Symposium & Manager Awards|url=http://creditflux.com/asset/documents/82dd92c8fb9355e995958dede4f50600.pdf|publisher=Creditflux|accessdate=8 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413113309/http://creditflux.com/asset/documents/82dd92c8fb9355e995958dede4f50600.pdf|archive-date=2015-04-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Davidson|first1=Tom|title=Recognizing the Best in Credit|url=http://creditflux.com/Newsletter/2014-05-29/Recognising-the-best-in-credit|publisher=Creditflux|accessdate=13 April 2015|date=29 May 2014|archive-date=2015-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413113010/http://creditflux.com/Newsletter/2014-05-29/Recognising-the-best-in-credit|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

==投资==

安祖高顿经营三种基本的投资工具类型：

* 非流动策略——包括不同的投资策略：不良证券、私募股权、三倍净租赁和房地产。
* 流动策略——信贷机遇、可转换套利及风险套利。
* 多策略——利用公司众多领域有吸引力的另类投资机遇。

